                    <MudText Typo="Typo.body2" class="mb-2">This will usher in a completely new approach to supply chain management allowing for Global Standards for Just-in-Time Deliveries allowing better planning of inventory, bringing down Global Shipping costs and ease of doing Business to all customers.</MudText>
                    <MudText Typo="Typo.body2" class="mb-2">We look forward to sharing our newest venture ITUP, with you</MudText>
